short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Kernet Hunt automaticaly extracts data from LinkedIn profiles

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Talent Acquisition made easier with Kernet Hunt Sourcing. One click in Linkedin and the candidate profile information will be imported into one or more job positions created in Kernet. Our browser extension is a complement to your account.
